            <title>[CASSANDRA-2929] Don&apos;t include tmp files as sstable when create column families</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2929</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When we open a column family and populate the SSTableReader, we happen to include -tmp files. This has no change to actually happen in a real life situation, but that is what was triggering a race in the unit tests triggering spurious assertion failure in estimateRowsFromIndex.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
